{"id":580852,"date":[{"year":1979,"month":7,"day":4}],"page":"4","source":"《解放军文艺》","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"241","ytitle":"","mtitle":"战士的颂歌","ftitle":"","authors":["陈沂"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈沂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念党的58生日，步叶帅八十书怀原韵呈华主席、叶、邓副主席."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、呈华主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息传来鼓乐兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州又有掌舵人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三分世界承先策"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海人民步后尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治国抓纲苏疾苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时艰受命拯危沦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘夜夜京华梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北斗当空分外明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、呈叶副主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高龄八十系衰兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党国元戎不后人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满眼烽烟观世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥天劫火炼寰尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运筹若定肖曹逊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈笑之间权霸沦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士难忘十万里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心如火到天明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、呈邓副主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全会开来大业兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九洲物望在斯人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"襟怀坦荡深如海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风骨嶙峥不染尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动地妖氛头可断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如磐风雨志难沦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁言功过千秋定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片丹心日月明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(原载七月号《解放军文艺》)"}]}